🧠 Viva Quick Answers
👉 What is CI?
Continuous Integration – automatically testing code when pushed.

👉 What is GitHub Actions?
Automation tool to run workflows like testing and deployment.

👉 What is Docker used for here?
To package Python app into a container.

👉 Why pytest?
To test correctness of code.

👉 What are secrets?
Secure variables like passwords stored in GitHub.

